subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Suzann Pettersen birdied the final two holes for a three-under-par 69 and shared the first-round lead with Meena Lee in the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Hana Bank Kolon Championship in Gyeongju, South Korea. Four players were at 71.
